ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with 2814986 Ontario Inc. ** NCC **
PrecisOrder approving that National Capital Commission enter into a lease agreement with 2814986 Ontario Inc. for a period of 99 years, for real property located at 1460 Riverside Drive, in Ottawa, Ontario, for a development in accordance with municipal zoning and federal land use approvals.
